rows.label: qst200817_msg0001
rows.name:
Get out of the way! Do
you want to get hurt?!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0002
rows.name:
You put out the fire we went
to the trouble of lighting!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0003
rows.name:
No! I won't let you
burn any more trees!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0004
rows.name:
What are you talking about! This
has nothing to do with you!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0005
rows.name: If you don't move, you'll get hurt!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0006
rows.name:
The Saffronia trees are also important
to the residents of Fons Maim!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0007
rows.name:
We won't forgive you
for harming the trees!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0008
rows.name:
This is a pain! Let's
get them all at once!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0009
rows.name:
We're Invidians too. We've
received combat training.

rows.label: qst200817_msg0010
rows.name: You won't get away unscathed either!

rows.label: qst200817_msg0011
rows.name:
Everyone... were you
protecting the trees...?

rows.label: qst200817_msg0012
rows.name:
There are so many people
who cherish nature...

rows.label: qst200817_msg0014
rows.name:
Yes! I will protect these
people and the great tree!
